text: Raúl Caldeira (born 21 January 1927) was a Portuguese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Portugal Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
